metadata.name: Freyja Rae, Aqua Douse
metadata.description:
"In a blur of movement, a burst of sunlight, and a splattering of water, Freyja Rae de Vil becomes a total mood with an unbelievable gaze, and hits an electrifying pose that stops this moment in time in such a way that transcends everything I could have ever expected or wanted."

This is the very first NFT ever offered by Nino Batista, minted on October 10, 2022.
